s://lihkg.com/thread/1426739/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好搞TVB呀，和平呼籲佢地罷工啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1422849/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1422849/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 你地繼續叫林鄭下台啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417341/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417341/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1418035/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1418035/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417281/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417281/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1416814/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1416814/page/1</a><br />\n事實：林鄭下台其實都無撚用<br />\n<br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好登報，用啲錢做其他野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346745/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346745/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好成立臨時政府<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1232468/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1232468/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好搞G20登報，搞7.1啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1257157/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1257157/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好沖(殘體字)立法會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1271370/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1271370/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 五大訴求係on9<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1305986/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1305986/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 警察可能會全面驅趕鄉黑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1342662/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1342662/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 繼續和平遊行啦~<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1353893/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1353893/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 說服警察加入遊行，感化警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1230663/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1230663/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 整多個G牌啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434492/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434492/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 【急】而家真係需要一個大台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1337502/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1337502/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBruce.Lee P牌仔 起底頁面傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/258370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/258370</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推上熱門"},{"pid":"55bb1d96241f48f3c6b871d08f2cd8cf6885ec56","tid":1452264,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:41:02.000Z","msg":"自推10下 4/10"},{"pid":"232c64fa6ca0bca88754a58f72e2e7297d13132d","tid":1452264,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:41:43.000Z","msg":"自推10下 5/10"},{"pid":"076a51a9ecd1f5a3e399af476fe9acb805b1d32b","tid":1452264,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:43:29.000Z","msg":"自推10下 6/10"},{"pid":"063ed37a6246ee2d9b551bc55d2066c984284a87","tid":1452264,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:43:43.000Z","msg":"自推10下 7/10"},{"pid":"68cdbf32b7b721e877b9791d70127fb2ad67e46a","tid":1452264,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:43:56.000Z","msg":"自推10下 8/10"},{"pid":"74e4264bb24f6cf184965a0f4bc4b5db36abec99","tid":1452264,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:44:15.000Z","msg":"自推10下 9/10"},{"pid":"ffadeb3dece5fd6cf3b0b6d914640fd242879a74","tid":1452264,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:44:25.000Z","msg":"自推10下 10/10"}]}